net.proteusframework.internet.http.resource

Interface ClassPathResourceLibrary

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    PublicLibrary

    public interface ClassPathResourceLibrary
    Defines an interface that enums that resource libraries available through a ClassPathResourceFactory should implement.
    Author:
    Pat B. Double (double@i2rd.com), Russ Tennant (russ@i2rd.com) (based on CMS ClassPathResourceLibrary)
